extends layout

block content
    .page.js-page
      // One Page Sidebar
      .one-page-sidebar
        // One Page Sidebar Header
        .one-page-sidebar-header
          // One Page Logo
          .one-page-logo
            // Logo Image
            a.logo-image(href='/hr_managers')
              img(src='/images/logo2.png')
            br
            a.logo-image(href='/hr_managers')
              img(src='/images/manager.png')
        .one-page-nav-wrapper.js-custom-scrollbar
          ul.one-page-nav.js-one-page-nav(data-prepend-to='.js-prepend-mobile-menu')
            li.is-active
              a(href='#what')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-user-md
                | Role of the Manager
            li
              a(href='#add_manager')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-user-plus
                | Add Manager
            li
              a(href='#resend_credentials')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-send
                | Resend Credentials
            li
              a(href='#delete_manager')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-trash
                | Delete Manager
        // End of One Page Nav
        // One Page Sidebar Footer
        footer.one-page-sidebar-footer
          | All Rights Reserved.
          a(href='http://www.masymbol.com/', target='_blank') Masymbol Technologies
          |  Pvt Ltd © 2016
        // End of One Page Sidebar Footer
      // End of One Page Sidebar
      // One Page Content
      .one-page-content
        // Header
        header.header.large.header-one-page.js-header-fixed
          .container-fluid.container-spaced
            .row
              .col-md-3.col-sm-6.col-xs-5
                .visible-sm-block.visible-xs-block
                  // Logo Image
                  a.logo-image(href='/')
                    img.img-responsive(src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/skilledtree-public/logo.png', alt='logo')
                  // End of Logo Image
              .col-md-9.col-sm-6.col-xs-7
                // Menu
                nav.right.helper
                  ul.menu.sf-menu.js-menu
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_managers')
                        i.fa.fa-home.fa-lg
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_managers/introduction')
                        | Introduction
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_managers/team') Team
                    li
                      a.active(href='#') Members
                      ul
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/employees') Employees
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/recruiter') Recruiter
                        li
                          a.active(href='/hr_managers/manager') Manager
                    li
                      a(href='#') Jobs
                      ul
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/Jobs') Jobs
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/resumes') Resumes
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_managers/gamification') Gamification
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_managers/reports') Reports
                    li
                      a(href='#') Branding
                      ul
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/career') Career Page
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/companybrand') Company Branding
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_managers/dashboard') Dashboard
                    li
                      a(href='#') Header
                      ul
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/header') Header Icons
                        li
                          a(href='/hr_managers/settings') Settings
                // End of Menu
        // End of Header
        #content
          .container-fluid.container-spaced
            .col-md-12
              // Category Info
              #what.category-info.helper.pt0
                br
                h1 Role of the Manager
                p.category-content
                  | Manager can only view the jobs and it’s resumes which are posted and assigned in his team. Manager can’t do all the activities like HRs instead he can view the resumes to screen them before scheduling an interview.
            .col-md-12
              #add_manager.category-info.helper.pt0
                br
                h1
                  | Add Manager
                p.category-content
                  | Before adding manager, Make sure that you have added ‘Team’ in the ‘Settings’ section. ‘Default’ team is added when you create your organization account in SkilledTree. Name, Email and Team can be added by the HR Manager in the ‘Management’ section. One or more managers can be added at a single time by clicking ‘Add more’ button. Login credentials will be sent to his/her email client.
            .row
              .col-md-8
                img(src='/images/addmanager.png', width='100%')
            .col-md-12
              #resend_credentials.category-info.helper.pt0
                br
                h1
                  | Resend Credentials
                p.category-content
                  | You can search the recruiter by entering their email in the search box given there in ‘Recruiter’ under Management section.
            .col-md-12
              #delete_manager.category-info.helper.pt0
                br
                h1
                  | Delete Manager
                p.category-content
                  | If you want to move a recruiter from one team to another team, this can be possible by clicking the editable dropdown in the Recruiter's List which is right below on ‘Recruiter’ section.
    // End of One Page Content
